*.spl
.DS_Store
__pycache__/
stage/
dist/

# editor swap/temp files (can contain secrets — never commit)
*.swp
*.swo
.*.sw?
*~

# ingest state / creds (repo-only tooling; NEVER commit)
# NOTE: bare names match at ANY depth (repo ROOT *and* tools/); the **/ and /.env
# forms are explicit belt-and-suspenders so root-level creds can never leak.
.env
/.env
**/.env
oura_targets.json
**/oura_targets.json
oura_tokens.json
**/oura_tokens.json
oura_checkpoint.json
oura_dedup_store.json
oura_sync.lock
*.tmp
